item.title: How To Make iPhone Apps Faster | My Custom Workflow [Swift 5, Xcode 12] - Aryaman Sharda
item.description:
Check out my eBook - Ace The iOS Interview (https://aryamansharda.gumroad.com/l/tcvck)
I released my first app on the App Store back in 2013 and it took me 3 months to make and it was absolutely awful. Since then I've improved a lot and had the opportunity to work on dozens of iOS apps both professionally and personally as side projects.
So, I wanted to share my current workflow for quickly ideating and creating new iOS apps and show you how I was able to release my last 3 iOS apps from start to finish in just one week, respectively.
We'll cover my ideation process, my development tools, and my post-launch analytics workflows as well.
Blog: https://digitalbunker.dev/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/aryamansharda
